"freedb tab Hejuru Ukwihuza Kuri A Ibaruwa Seriveri: Kuri Tanga Gishya "
"<acronym> </acronym> Ibyinjijwe . ni NIBA OYA Sisitemu Nka A Seriveri: . "
"<guilabel> Icyoherejwe Biturutse </guilabel> Kuri Koresha iyi Ikiranga . "

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:135
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you plan to submit a CDDB entry, enter your email address into the first "
"textbox."
msgstr ""

