"Byose Imitwe na i <guilabel> : </guilabel> na <guilabel> </guilabel> "
"Amashami: Byuzuye Inyuma , Kanda i <guibutton> </guibutton> Akabuto Kuri "
"Kohereza Icyoherejwe ku e - Ibaruwa Kuri freedb . "

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:183
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You will be prompted to select a category for the submission. The "
"<guilabel>Disc ID</guilabel> section displays the 32 bit <acronym>ID</"
"acronym> code used by freedb to identify a compact disc. Above the "
"<acronym>ID</acronym> code is the category of the <guilabel>freedb</"
"guilabel> entry. These categories correspond to the subfolders tree of the "
"folder chosen in the <guilabel>freedb Base Folder:</guilabel> in the <link "
"linkend=\"cddb-page\"><guilabel>CDDB</guilabel> page</link> of the "
"configuration window."
msgstr ""
"Kuri Guhitamo A Icyiciro ya:  i Icyoherejwe . <guilabel> </guilabel> "
"Icyiciro i 32 <acronym> </acronym> Inyandikoporogaramu Byakoreshejwe ku "
"freedb Kuri Kugaragaza A DISIKI . i <acronym> </acronym> Inyandikoporogaramu "
"ni i Icyiciro Bya i <guilabel> freedb </guilabel> Icyinjijwe . Ibyiciro Kuri "
"i &Igiti Bya i Ububiko... in i <guilabel> freedb Base : </guilabel> in i "
"<link linkend=\"freedb-tab\"> <guilabel> freedb </guilabel> tab </link> Bya "
"i &kscd; Idirishya . "

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:193
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Length:</guilabel> display shows the total play time of the "
"&CD;."
