"<guilabel> : </guilabel> Kugaragaza: i Igiteranyo: %S Gukina Igihe Bya i "
"&CD; . "

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:196
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Press the <guibutton>Fetch Info</guibutton> button to download "
"<acronym>CDDB</acronym> data. Press the <guibutton>OK</guibutton> button to "
"save your changes locally. The <guibutton>Cancel</guibutton> button closes "
"the &CD; Database Editor without saving."
msgstr ""
"i <guibutton> </guibutton> Akabuto Kuri Iyimura <acronym> </acronym> "
"Ibyatanzwe . i <guibutton> </guibutton> Akabuto Kuri Kubika Amahinduka . "
